title: Werewolf By Night Could Be The Future of Marvel
description:
MERCH: https://standard.tv/collections/captain-midnight
Werewolf By Night is an interesting experiment from the MCU that Marvel put on Disney Plus recently. In this video I go over the adventures of Jack Russell, Ted and Elsa Bloodstone and how it could impact the future of the Marvel Cinematic Universe.
Music by Epidemic Sound (http://www.epidemicsound.com)
